  "body": "### Describe the bug\r\n\r\nSee [AbstractJpaOperations#persist(Stream)](https://github.com/quarkusio/quarkus/blob/ebd6d377ea432bdc13bed47b72cb46387a7f9bbe/extensions/panache/hibernate-reactive-panache-common/runtime/src/main/java/io/quarkus/hibernate/reactive/panache/common/runtime/AbstractJpaOperations.java#L96)\r\n\r\n\r\nThe Hibernate Reactive session cannot be used this way or it might lead to errors that are hard to debug.\r\nInstead, the persist operations should be chained  so that the execution is sequential.\r\nSee the [documentation on GitHub](https://github.com/hibernate/hibernate-reactive/blob/main/documentation/src/main/asciidoc/reference/introduction.adoc#sessions-and-vertx-contexts):\r\n> The session is not thread-safe (or \"stream-safe\"), so using it across different threads (or reactive streams) may cause bugs that are extremely hard to detect\r\n\r\n",
